scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Some page numbers are non-sequential, though the narrative appears sequential; others have been marked through and changed, sometimes twice. Pages include 216-223, which have been changed to 195-202; 218, 219, 220, 220A, and 221, which are renumbered twice as 224-228 and 203-207; and 229-254, which are renumbered as 209-234 (with some of these pages renumbered yet again, ending the chapter with three different numbers: 254 and 234 and 237).
